---
---
<!-- Testimonials -->
<section class="py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 mb-16 text-center reveal">
        <span class="text-gold font-semibold text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Bukti Nyata</span>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl text-primary">Apa Kata Wali Santri?</h2>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Horizontal Scroll Container -->
    <div class="flex gap-6 overflow-x-auto pb-8 hide-scrollbar px-6 md:px-12 snap-x snap-mandatory max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="shrink-0 w-[300px] md:w-[400px] snap-center bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-border/50 reveal">
            <div class="flex text-gold mb-4 gap-1">
                {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => <span class="text-lg">★</span>)}
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted italic mb-6">"Alhamdulillah, sejak mondok di sini, perubahan adab putri kami sangat terlihat. Hafalannya lancar berkat bimbingan intensif yang disiplin namun penuh rasa kasih sayang."</p>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary">Bapak Arief</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted">Wali Santri Program Tahfidz</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="shrink-0 w-[300px] md:w-[400px] snap-center bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-border/50 reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="flex text-gold mb-4 gap-1">
                {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => <span class="text-lg">★</span>)}
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted italic mb-6">"Lingkungan asrama di Pujon sangat sejuk dan aman. Saya merasa sangat tenang menitipkan putri kami di asrama yang bersih dan terjaga secara islami."</p>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary">Ibu Fatimah</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted">Wali Santri Madrasah Aliyah</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="shrink-0 w-[300px] md:w-[400px] snap-center bg-background p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-border/50 reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="flex text-gold mb-4 gap-1">
                {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => <span class="text-lg">★</span>)}
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted italic mb-6">"Perpaduan pelajaran kitab salaf dan keahlian keputrian seperti agribisnis minimalis (TETRIS) sangat mendidik kemandirian anak kami untuk masa depannya."</p>
            <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary">Bapak Susanto</h4>
                <p class="text-xs text-muted">Wali Santri Madrasah Diniyyah</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
